  "detailed_description": "<i>Legends say that the one who succeeds in climbing the tower of God will be granted a wish. Will you be the one to succeed?</i><br><br>Tower of God is a match-3 game with fun mechanics and enjoyable Game play. The levels are varied and fun. The game also includes mini-games such as Hidden Object, Jigsaw, Memory and Slider.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pick up and play<br></li><li>100 levels of fun match making<br></li><li>Fun mini games included<br></li><li>New types of runes and tiles<br></li><li>Climb the tower of God!</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<i>Legends say that the one who succeeds in climbing the tower of God will be granted a wish. Will you be the one to succeed?</i><br><br>Tower of God is a match-3 game with fun mechanics and enjoyable Game play. The levels are varied and fun. The game also includes mini-games such as Hidden Object, Jigsaw, Memory and Slider.<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Pick up and play<br></li><li>100 levels of fun match making<br></li><li>Fun mini games included<br></li><li>New types of runes and tiles<br></li><li>Climb the tower of God!</li></ul>",
